《極地詭變》獲得的評價並不佳。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於149條評論，新鮮度36%，平均評分5.1／10<ref>{{Rotten-tomatoes|the_thing_2011|The Thing}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]獲得49分，負評居多<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-thing| title = The Thing Reviews| work = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]]| accessdate = October 14, 2011| archive-date = 2011-10-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111008215452/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-thing| dead-url = no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落於「B-」<ref>{{Cite web|author=Pamela McClintock|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-footloose-grosses-248906|title='Box Office Report: 'Footloose' Grosses $5.57 Million, On Course To Dance Away With The Weekend – The Hollywood Reporter:|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2011-10-14|accessdate=2011-10-14|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201020023/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-footloose-grosses-248906|dead-url=no}}</ref>，觀眾的反應比影評人好上一些。

=== 票房 ===
《極地詭變》在開幕的周末總計849萬3665美元，最終在票房榜上排名第三。電影被分配到2996個影院，在前10名排行榜上只維持一個星期，在第二個星期則下降到第16名。關於結論國內的營運額總計1692萬美元<ref name="boxofficemojo">{{Cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=thing11.htm |title=The Thing (2011) (2011) – Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2016-12-20 |archive-date=2012-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106221051/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=thing11.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它於[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]上評論為「徹底的失望」自然處於劣勢，並繼續說著：「《極地詭變》並沒有給予未看過《突》的觀眾預期的看好，因此只能留給已經熟悉《突》概念元素的影迷們開始大量出現。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3292 |title=Weekend Report: Remakes Can't Retire 'Real Steel' – Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2016-12-20 |archive-date=2011-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111020080848/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3292 |dead-url=no }}</ref>」，這部電影在國外賺取了953萬美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=thing11.htm |title=The Thing (2011) (2011) – International Box Office Results – Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2016-12-20 |archive-date=2012-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106004841/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=thing11.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，到目前為止全球總票房總額為2742萬8670美元。<ref name="boxofficemojo"/>

